- Integration
- Support and Maintenance

The Global 5G System Integration Market can be segmented based on components and services. When it comes to components, the market is divided into hardware and software. Hardware includes the physical equipment required to build and deploy 5G networks, such as antennas, base stations, and routers. On the other hand, software refers to the programs and applications that enable the functioning of these hardware components. In terms of services, the market is segmented into consulting, integration, and support and maintenance. Consulting services help in designing and strategizing the implementation of 5G systems, while integration services assist in the seamless integration of various components. Support and maintenance services ensure the smooth operation and upkeep of 5G networks.

